{"tid":1604883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10-1 大家練好呼吸法未？","createTime":"2019-09-30T06:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T06:22:19.000Z","uid":253343,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71d4221a7ecaab74cc344085ab549683b174153d","tid":1604883,"uid":253343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:03:40.000Z","msg":"柱（はしら）<br />\n鬼殺隊中最高等級的劍士，為鬼殺隊的柱石。這代共有「水」、「蟲」、「炎」、「音」、「岩」、「戀」、「霞」、「蛇」、「風」的9位流派劍士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和勇大合作   各有各做"},{"pid":"967ca4ec82a47d2c6ce84e612d2ac4746bbe414c","tid":1604883,"uid":253343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:05:19.000Z","msg":"隱（カクシ）<br />\n鬼殺隊裏不擔任戰鬥，只負責於劍士戰鬥後收尾工作的部隊成員，是由完全沒有劍術才能的人所組成，全員都身着黑子裝扮。和劍士之間並無上下等級之分。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後援重要性"},{"pid":"d53e787f3c860b930c2ab14735ef2c3c49796514","tid":1604883,"uid":253343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"繼子（つぐこ）<br />\n由柱親自培養的頂尖弟子。可以向柱提出申請，或受到柱的提拔，據說如果沒有非常優秀的才能是沒辦法成為繼子的，與該柱使用相同呼吸法當然是最好，但當中也有使用不同呼吸法或沒有任何呼吸法的繼子出現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n燈火不能熄滅"},{"pid":"c30eb96fd1471af24b971ecb7e5d55c948a8c6b0","tid":1604883,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"10-1水系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d8b93a578d67b4422eac325ffb5316ce4b0032","tid":1604883,"uid":224869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:10:36.000Z","msg":"徵哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/pigeonpatrol\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpigeonpatrol&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1egAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=b5c8c148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/pigeonpatrol</a>"},{"pid":"292ad0b5112c73e7023c3a6c3261fb3305dfbb66","tid":1604883,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"各位柱同隱<br />\n都要好好合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3d2b4